# Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your values.

```bash
cp .env.example .env.local
```

## Required Variables

```env
# Supabase (required)
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://ntjlbfkpyikabintxvnu.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJzdXBhYmFzZSIsInJlZiI6Im50amxiZmtweWlrYWJpbnR4dm51Iiwicm9sZSI6ImFub24iLCJpYXQiOjE3NzY5MzM3NTcsImV4cCI6MjA5MjUwOTc1N30.jwkQnq1-JxcbFMb4qV0IzIeoFP_xy9IYhFWv900Vfgk
SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJzdXBhYmFzZSIsInJlZiI6Im50amxiZmtweWlrYWJpbnR4dm51Iiwicm9sZSI6InNlcnZpY2Vfcm9sZSIsImlhdCI6MTc3NjkzMzc1NywiZXhwIjoyMDkyNTA5NzU3fQ.qTlThE6k0euwSYvzObRpHgGWxkP4EFsXEmEXBHwp5f4
# JWT Secret (REQUIRED - change this to a secure random string!)
JWT_SECRET=638406c4-0cc1-426b-a647-ac65920793cc

# Cron Job Security (optional, for protecting cron endpoints)
CRON_SECRET=your-cron-secret-key
```

## Optional Variables (for production features)

```env
# Twilio (SMS/WhatsApp alerts)
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=your-twilio-account-sid
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=your-twilio-auth-token
TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER=+1234567890

# SendGrid (Email alerts)
SENDGRID_API_KEY=your-sendgrid-api-key
SENDGRID_FROM_EMAIL=noreply@yourdomain.com
```

## Local Development

# For local development, create `.env.local` in the `frontend` folder:

# ```env
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY=your-service-role-key
# JWT_SECRET=dev-secret-key-change-in-production
# ```
